If your a casual gamer (not just thinking you can't get epic) then upgrading haste is of course more important.<br>
<br>
The actual last 4 fights for epic aren't that difficult and can be done with 1 or 2 decent groups except for the last one where you'll need 2 or 3 solid mid 50's groups. People usually don't mind helping out if you ask them as well. The fights (other then sky) are all pretty quick and easy. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#cccccc><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/utruyth.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Truyth</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Monk-in-Training</span><br>  Posts: 97<br> <font color=#8b1a1a>(10/18/02 8:39:37 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm3.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=11894.topic&index=4>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Would this be worth the Upgrade?</span><hr size=1> get your epic, its the best piece of gear you'll ever own. <p><a href=http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=463><i>Truyth</i></a></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub35.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm3.showPrevMessage?topicID=11894.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub35.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm3.showNextMessage?topicID=11894.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm3.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=11894.topic&index=3><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/addReply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm3.emailToFriend?topicID=11894.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm3.threadControl?topicID=11894.topic><img src=http://ww